  "description": "In the books, the titular Grandma seeks to explore the true meaning of the Japanese phrase \"mottainai\" after her son asked her what it meant and she couldn't answer. \"Mottainai\" is a commonly used exclamation that roughly translates to \"what a waste!\", expressing regret over wastefulness. The Grandma seeks to explore the meaning and importance of \"mottainai\" in the story.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)",
